Name: Verify that the electric bike’s break is working
Description: The purpose of this test case is to verify that the bike’s break can be turned on and manage to stop the bike from moving.
Preconditions: User has switched on the bike for driving.
Step by step actions to follow:
1.	Accelerate the speed and start moving
2.	Turn on the bike’s brake and notice if the speed is reducing
3.	Press the brake on its maximum to fully stop the bike
Expected outcome: The bike’s speed is reducing when pressing the bike and eventually the bike stops.
